node.text: Thank you @eagala for 20 years of providing solutions in mental health to so many deserving people all over the world. This video captures the Alex and Ani team in their first introduction to the process. We had the pleasure of participating in an EAGALA team building workshop where we worked on team work and communication. #CHARITYBYDESIGN #equinetherapy #mentalhealthawareness
